<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="cs">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>vondrart leady {{ summary.run_date }}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f4f4f5;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;color:#18181b;">
  <div style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px;">

    <h1 style="font-size:20px;margin:0 0 2px;">vondrart — denní leady</h1>
    <p style="margin:0 0 16px;color:#52525b;font-size:13px;">{{ summary.run_date }}</p>

    <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e4e4e7;border-radius:8px;padding:12px 16px;margin-bottom:20px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">
      <strong>{{ summary.shown }}</strong> {{ 'lead' if summary.shown == 1 else 'leadů' }} v digestu
      &middot; {{ summary.total_new }} nových celkem
      &middot; {{ summary.above_threshold }} nad prahem (skóre &ge; {{ summary.threshold }})
    </div>

    {% for lead in leads %}
    <div style="background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e4e4e7;border-radius:8px;padding:16px;margin-bottom:14px;">
      <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;">
        <tr>
          <td style="font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:top;">{{ lead.name }}</td>
          <td align="right" style="vertical-align:top;white-space:nowrap;">
            <span style="display:inline-block;background:#18181b;color:#ffffff;border-radius:999px;padding:2px 10px;font-size:13px;">
              {{ lead.score if lead.score is not none else '–' }}/10
            </span>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <p style="margin:8px 0 0;color:#52525b;font-size:13px;">
        {{ lead.obor or '—' }}
        {% if lead.region %}&middot; {{ lead.region }}{% endif %}
        {% if lead.date %}&middot; vznik {{ lead.date }}{% endif %}
        {% if lead.nace %}&middot; NACE {{ lead.nace | join(', ') }}{% endif %}
      </p>

      {% if lead.reason %}
      <p style="margin:10px 0 0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">{{ lead.reason }}</p>
      {% endif %}

      {% if lead.outreach_draft %}
      <div style="margin:12px 0 0;background:#f4f4f5;border-left:3px solid #18181b;border-radius:4px;padding:10px 12px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;white-space:pre-line;">
        <strong style="display:block;margin-bottom:4px;color:#3f3f46;">Návrh oslovení</strong>{{ lead.outreach_draft }}
      </div>
      {% endif %}

      {% if lead.url %}
      <p style="margin:12px 0 0;font-size:13px;">
        <a href="{{ lead.url }}" style="color:#2563eb;text-decoration:none;">Detail v ARES &rarr;</a>
      </p>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endfor %}

    {% if not leads %}
    <p style="font-size:14px;color:#52525b;">Dnes žádné nové leady.</p>
    {% endif %}

    <p style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a;line-height:1.5;margin-top:20px;">
      Drafty jsou jen podklad — koho a jak oslovit, rozhoduješ ty. Respektuj GDPR a pravidla
      pro nevyžádaná obchodní sdělení. Nic se leadům neodesílá automaticky.
    </p>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
